File Name: A220705 Zebra-8 電阻與螺絲short造成DUT shut down-3
Original Description:
7/1 夜班生產發現Function & Final 站有Ping DUT異常，複測率 8.5%(25/293)
確認NG品的PCB單體測試OK，排除PCBA打件不良的問題
將NG品的PCB再重新組上下蓋異常復發
將NG品加大扭力下鎖此顆螺絲，function與final站可pass
ME確認異常品螺柱高度、機殼厚度、平面度、螺絲高度、塑膠件厚度皆合規，排除來料不良
經解析確認為螺絲與電容(C812)/電桿(L9)元件干涉造成PCBA 3.3V電壓對地短路問題，使得DUT無法開機
至7/5為止，已嘗試將鎖附扭力調至上限(3.5 kgf-cm)，仍有類似問題持續發現 (螺絲扭力spec: 3+/-0.5kgf-cm)
Definition: 測試過程或結果顯示功能不符合預期（如 NG、fail）。

Original Description:
SMT IPQC發現烘烤後的PCBA放在靜電箱內未使用靜電泡棉盛裝。
不良率：100% (33/33)。
PD描述：因PCB可能殘留濕氣，造成拆除零件(U37)時會有爆板現象 (前批爆板4pcs)。 PE工程評估後告知PD需烘烤PCB。烤箱於off-line雷雕區離PCB維修區相距甚遠。PCB經120∘C/7HR烘烤降溫後，因仍有餘溫，OP怕溫度會影響泡棉因此暫時乘載於黑色靜電箱，並集中放置於線修區旁待PCB完全冷卻後，人員忘記將泡棉重新放入而繼續堆放於線修區旁。

File Name: A24008_8D Report - DNSK-MB1 Cold soldering defects escape to Customer-v2 Eng
Original Description:
1. On 2024/2/19, WNC ATP production line feedback that DNSK-MB1 product RF test fail which is caused by the location U1 component, and the failure rate is 5.27%(150/2,845).
SMT PE performed the investigation and analysis immediately.
2. It was found that solder joints of U1 and the surrounding RLC components are cold soldering with solder power through 3D magnifying glass, as confirmed that the RF test failure is caused by poor SMT soldering quality. Please refer to the Figure1 as below.
3. During the investigation we confirmed the risk scope was one SMT MO with Qty 9996pcs and the SMT production time is during 2/9 20:00-2/10 6:00 and produced at SMT L1201 line.
After the risk assessment we determined to quarantine and scraped all these defects. But on 3/14 We found that there are total 2,465pcs defective products had been shipped to customer on 2024/2/23 (Qty:241pcs) and 2024/3/2(Qty 2224pcs)
Definition: 測試過程或結果顯示功能不符合預期（如 NG、fail）。

File Name: H23010_Hold Shipment Notice_Broadcom RFIC BCM43794B0IFFBG hang-up under low temperature
Original Description:
AP5050D S2 PCBA returned and applied HASA verification on 2/15, found Wi-Fi SSID Missing at 5G under low temperature at -40 degree C.  
This failure symptom is related to CPU (U63, BCM49418B0IFEBG_SoC) or RFIC (BCM43794B0IFFBG_U14-2G/U26-5G/U77-6G) malfunction. RD team adopts HW/SW/Environment/Combined Tests to clarify root cause,  it is considered the root cause is caused by RFIC at  the temperature down to -35 degree C.  
Further 2pcs AP5050U (Built by S1) were verified and found one DUT also failed at Low Temperature.
The symptom of RFIC could be resolved by restarting its interface.  NG DC: 2205/ CCZ0507700.
